Plot: Carmella was fresh out of the University, starting her adult life with everything ahead of her. When she found a great house in her ancestral home of Window Rock, Arizona, she was thrilled. Everything seemed perfect, and she couldn’t wait to learn about the Navajo ways and her mother’s role in their life. She soon finds a book of spells and after that, she finds herself being taunted by a deceased Skinwalker that tries to take the life that she's got left.
